import React from "react" const LoginAndBooking =()=> { return(

    Devotees can login with either Mobile Number and OTP/password or Email ID and password.


    Same Mobile number or Email ID used for creating an account cannot be used for different accounts.


    After login, devotees should update their personal details - Name, Age, ID proof to book services.


    Details of any one of the Photo IDs - Aadhar Card/ Voter ID/PAN CARD/PASSPORT/RATION CARD/ DRIVING LICENCE to be entered which will be verified at Shirdi while availing services.




) } export default LoginAndBooking;
